l%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%20and%20sent%20global%20markets%20into%20a%20tailspin.%20Trump's%20plan%20included%20a%20baseline%2010%25%20tariff%20on%20all%20countries%20and%20higher%20tariffs%20on%20countries%20the%20White%20House%20considered%20%26quot%3Bthe%20worst%20offenders%26quot%3B%20in%20US%20trade%20relations.%20Israel%2C%20one%20of%20the%20US's%20major%20non-NATO%20allies%2C%20faces%20a%2017%25%20tariff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20eliminate%20the%20trade%20deficit%20with%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20Netanyahu%20told%20reporters%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%20following%20a%20private%20meeting%20with%20Trump.%20%26quot%3BWe%20intend%20to%20do%20it%20very%20quickly.%20We%20think%20it's%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do.%20And%20we're%20going%20to%20also%20eliminate%20trade%20barriers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsrael%20can%20serve%20as%20a%20model%20for%20many%20countries%20who%20ought%20to%20do%20the%20same%2C%26quot%3B%20Netanyahu%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20free-trade%20champion%2C%20and%20free%20trade%20has%20to%20be%20fair%20trade.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20the%20US%20exported%20%2414.8%20billion%20worth%20of%20goods%20to%20Israel%20and%20imported%20%2422.2%20billion%20worth%20of%20goods%20from%20Israel%2C%20totaling%20a%20%247.4%20billion%20goods%20trade%20deficit%20for%20the%20year%2C%20an%208.6%25%20increase%20from%202023%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fustr.gov%2Fcountries-regions%2Feurope-middle-east%2Fmiddle-eastnorth-africa%2Fisrael%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIsrael%2520Trade%2520Summary%2C(%25241.4%2520billion)%2520from%25202023.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20trade%20data%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20three%20main%20goods%20that%20Israel%20exported%20to%20the%20US%20were%20diamonds%2C%20integrated%20circuits%20(also%20known%20as%20microchips)%2C%20and%20broadcasting%20equipment%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F