E-%20China%20responds%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing%20hit%20back%2C%20saying%20in%20a%20statement%20from%20its%20US%20embassy%20that%20%26quot%3Bpressuring%20or%20threatening%20China%20is%20not%20a%20right%20way%20to%20engage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStock%20markets%20and%20oil%20prices%20collapsed%20further%2C%20as%20trading%20floors%20across%20the%20world%20endured%20waves%20of%20selling%20after%20last%20week's%20sharp%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWall%20Street%20stocks%20finished%20lower%20following%20a%20volatile%20session%2C%20with%20both%20the%20Dow%20and%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20ending%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Hong%20Kong%20collapsed%20by%2013.2%20percent%20Monday%2C%20its%20worst%20day%20in%20nearly%20three%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrillions%20of%20dollars%20have%20been%20wiped%20off%20combined%20stock%20market%20valuations%20in%20recent%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETokyo%20closed%20down%20by%20almost%20eight%20percent.%20Frankfurt%20fell%20as%20much%20as%2010%20percent%20in%20early%20trading%20before%20paring%20back%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20doubled%20down%20again%20on%20Monday%2C%20saying%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20looking%26quot%3B%20at%20any%20pause%20in%20tariff%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20scrapped%20any%20meetings%20with%20China%20over%20tariffs%2C%20but%20said%20the%20United%20States%20was%20ready%20for%20talks%20with%20any%20country%20willing%20to%20negotiate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20can%20be%20permanent%20tariffs%2C%20and%20there%20can%20also%20be%20negotiations%2C%20because%20there%20are%20things%20that%20we%20need%20beyond%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20while%20meeting%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20the%20first%20leader%20to%20lobby%20him%20in%20person%20over%20the%20levies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2010%20percent%20%26quot%3Bbaseline%26quot%3B%20tariff%20on%20US%20imports%20from%20around%20the%20world%20took%20effect%20Saturday