ys%20characters%20Smoke%20and%20Stack%20in%20%26quot%3BSinners.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EWarner%20Bros.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20filmmaker%20explained%20that%20the%20idea%20came%20from%20the%20story%20itself%2C%20which%2C%20vampires%20and%20gore%20aside%2C%20follows%20two%20brothers%20(both%20played%20by%20Jordan)%20who%20take%20over%20a%20juke%20joint%20in%20heavily%20racist%201930s%20Mississippi.%20Owning%20a%20film%20about%20Black%20ownership%20was%20a%20meaningful%20sticking%20point%20for%20Coogler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20the%20only%20motivation%2C%26quot%3B%20Coogler%20said%20of%20wanting%20the%20movie%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoogler%20said%20the%20movie%20was%20inspired%20by%20his%20grandfather%2C%20whom%20he%20never%20knew%20and%20who%20was%20from%20Mississippi%2C%20and%20his%20uncle%2C%20who%20died%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20uncle%20James%20loved%20to%20do%20three%20things%3A%20listening%20to%20Delta%20blues%20music%2C%20he%20loved%20drinking%20all%20types%20of%20whiskey%2C%20and%20he%20loved%20the%20San%20Francisco%20Giants%2C%20watching%20them%20on%20TV%20and%20listening%20to%20them%20on%20the%20radio%2C%26quot%3B%20Coogler%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20if%20you%20went%20and%20spent%20time%20with%20him%20he%20was%20doing%20one%20or%20all%20three%20of%20those%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20act%20of%20listening%20to%20that%20music%20and%20feeling%20he%20was%20there%20with%20me%20is%20kind%20of%20what%20inspired%20the%20period%20setting%20and%20the%20blues.%20And%20that%20is%20why%20the%20movie%20is%20so%20personal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoogler%20said%20%26quot%3BSinners%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20first%20feature%20film%20he's%20made%20that%20he'll%20own.%20But%20does%20he%20plan%20to%20own%20his%20films%20going%20forward%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%2C%20it%20was%20this%20specific%20project%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BSinners%26quot%3B