always%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20wait%20two%20to%20three%20days%20in%20between%20shampooing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20an%20excuse%20to%20give%20myself%20a%20good%20scalp%20massage%2C%20and%20once%20I%20rubbed%20the%20product%20in%2C%20the%20skin%20on%20my%20scalp%20felt%20noticeably%20less%20tight%20and%20dry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20applied%20the%20treatment%20on%20wet%20hair%20and%20then%20blow-dried%20it%2C%20I%20noticed%20a%20slight%20boost%20in%20shine%20and%20volume%20at%20the%20root.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20perks%20weren't%20quite%20as%20obvious%20when%20I%20applied%20it%20to%20dry%20hair%2C%20but%20I%20will%20say%20that%20I%20found%20it%20much%20easier%20to%20massage%20evenly%20into%20my%20scalp%20when%20my%20hair%20wasn't%20wet.%20I%20also%20felt%20a%20subtle%20cooling%20sensation%20on%20my%20scalp%20when%20I%20applied%20it%20to%20dry%20hair%2C%20which%20I%20certainly%20didn't%20hate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220cb9710e-2bdb-40c8-bc0c-59cdf32fbc10%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Ingredients%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOlaplex%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENo.0.5%20%3Cstrong%3EScalp%20Longevity%20Treatment%20ingredients%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20hand%20holding%20the%20Olaplex%20Scalp%20Longevity%20Treatment%20bottle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f41f9fc6ad288d147d6fad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Strong%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20researching%20the%20Olaplex%20No.0.5%20Scalp%20Longevity%20Treatment%20formula's%20ingredients%2C%20I%20admit%20I'm%20impressed%3A%20every%20single%20one%20appears%20to%20serve%20a%20function%20%E2%80%94%20no%20fillers%20here.%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20find%20that%20not%20only%20are%20many%20of%20these%20ingredients%20nourishing%20for%20the%20scalp%2C%20but%20they%20may%20also%20help%20to%20play%20a%20role%20in%20supporting%20hair%20growth.%20I%20also%20appreciate%20that%20this%20scalp%20treatment%20doesn't%20contain%20any%20artificial%20fragrances%2C%20which%20can%20be%20super%20irritating%20to%20sensitive%20skin%20like%20mine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20standout%20ingredients%20in%20the%20Olaplex%20Scalp%20Longevity%20Treatment%2C%20along%20with%20some%20of%20the%20benefits%20they%20offer%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBis-aminopropyl%20diglycol%20dimaleate%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20is%20the%20patented%20ingredient%20used%20in%20all%20Olaplex.%20It%20works%20by%20reconnecting%20and%20strengthening%20broken%20disulfide%20bonds%20in%20the%20hair%20that%20have%20been%20damaged%20by%20exposure%20to%20excessive%20heat%2C%20chemical%20treatments%2C%20environmental%20aggressors%2C%20and%20rough%20handling.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EArginine%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F376675262_Impaired_Arginine_Metabolism_in_Hair_Follicles_A_Potential_Mechanism_in_Androgenetic_Alopecia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStudies%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20shown%20that%20a%20deficiency%20in%20this%20amino%20acid%20is%20associated%20with%20hair%20loss.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F320843922_DIVERSE_POTENTIAL_AND_PHARMACOLOGICAL_STUDIES_OF_ARGININE%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResearchers%3C%2Fa%3E%20believe%20that%20arginine%20may%20be%20beneficial%20because%20it%20can%20improve%20blood%20supply%20to%20the%20hair%20roots%2C%20thereby%20stimulating%20growth%2C%20and%20also%20because%20it%20has%20a%20protective%20effect%20against%20damage.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERice%20bran%20oil%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjddonline.com%2Farticles%2Fa-systematic-review-application-of-rice-products-for-hair-growth-S1545961622P0177X%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2022%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20when%20applied%20topically%2C%20rice%20bran%20extracts%20can%20promote%20hair%20growth%20by%20curbing%20inflammation%2C%20reducing%20the%20enzyme%20that%20shortens%20the%20hair%20growth%20cycle%20and%20causes%20hair%20follicles%20to%20shrink%2C%20and%20increasing%20cell%20growth%20during%20the%20anagen%20phase%20%E2%80%94%20during%20which%20hair%20is%20actively%20growing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHydrogenated%20polydecene%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20ingredient%20acts%20as%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmy.clevelandclinic.org%2Fhealth%2Ftreatments%2F23305-emollients%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemollient%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20meaning%20that%20it%20can%20prevent%20moisture%20loss%2C%20soothe%20irritated%20skin%2C%20soften%20dry%20skin%2C%20and%20soften%20peeling%20or%20scaling%20skin.%20Emollients%20are%20often%20recommended%20to%20help%20treat%20eczema%2C%20psoriasis%2C%20and%20dermatitis.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGlycerin%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aad.org%2Fpublic%2Feveryday-care%2Fskin-care-basics%2Fcare%2Fwinter-skin-survival-kit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Academy%20of%20Dermatology%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%20calls%20glycerin%20one%20of%20the%20best%20ingredients%20for%20dry%20skin.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F5339621_Glycerol_and_the_skin_Holistic_approach_to_its_origin_and_functions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20shown%20that%20glycerin%20can%20increase%20skin%20hydration%20levels%2C%20protect%20the%20skin%20from%20irritation%2C%20and%20strengthen%20an%20impaired%20skin%20barrier%20function.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoybean%20seed%20extract%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESome%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC8947969%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudies%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggest%20that%20topical%20application%20of%20soybean%20extracts%20can%20reduce%20hair%20loss.%20In%20fact%2C%20researchers%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F39749369%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexploring%20the%20use%20of%20soybean%20extract%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20viable%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fminoxidil-alternatives-for-hair-growth-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealternative%20for%20prescription%20hair%20loss%20medications%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20minoxidil%20and%20finasteride%2C%20which%20are%20associated%20with%20some%20unpleasant%20side%20effects.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECeramide%20NP%2Fceramide%20EOP%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhealth.clevelandclinic.org%2Fceramides%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHalf%20of%20the%20epidermis%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20outer%20layer%20of%20your%20skin%20%E2%80%94%20is%20made%20up%20of%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Enaturally%20occurring%20fats%20known%20as%20ceramides.%20They%20play%20an%20important%20part%20in%20maintaining%20hydration%20and%20shielding%20the%20skin%20from%20toxins%20and%20irritants.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatchouli%20(pogostemon%20cablin)%20extract%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F373998125_Psychobiotics-like_Activity_as_a_Novel_Treatment_against_Dry_Scalp_Related-White_Flakes_Production_with_Pogostemon_cablin_Leaf_Extract%23pf19%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2023%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20applying%20this%20particular%20plant%20extract%20to%20the%20scalp%20helped%20to%20normalize%20sebum%20levels%20on%20the%20skin%2C%20balance%20the%20scalp%20microbiome%2C%20and%20increase%20the%20presence%20of%20certain%20bacteria%20that%20are%20crucial%20for%20a%20strong%20skin%20barrier.%20It's%20worth%20noting%20that%20an%20imbalance%20of%20sebum%20production%20is%20associated%20with%20common%20scalp%20issues%20like%20dandruff%20and%20seborrheic%20dermatitis.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELeptospermum%20scoparium%20branch%2Fleaf