20it%20would%20come%20in.%20Even%20when%20I%20did%20my%20best%20to%20budget%2C%20something%20always%20came%20up%2C%20like%20needing%20to%20buy%20something%20to%20wear%20for%20an%20event%20or%20having%20to%20split%20the%20bill%20with%20friends%20at%20a%20restaurant.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20began%20to%20think%20a%20lot%20about%20what%20my%20future%20would%20hold%20if%20I%20continued%20to%20live%20in%20Miami.%20Even%20after%20graduation%2C%20I%20couldn't%20see%20a%20lot%20changing%20as%20far%20as%20finances%20went.%20I'd%20likely%20be%20renting%20forever%2C%20unable%20to%20save%20up%20for%20a%20house.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20what%20bothered%20me%20the%20most%20was%20the%20amount%20of%20pressure%20I%20felt.%20Since%20I%20could%20never%20save%20up%20any%20money%2C%20I%20worried%20about%20how%20quickly%20things%20could%20go%20wrong%20if%20I%20got%20sick%20even%20for%20just%20a%20week%20and%20couldn't%20go%20to%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22df74aee7-ff91-489f-90cd-d8f123a7e64d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20made%20a%20dramatic%20change%20in%20order%20to%20lower%20my%20expenses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20this%20time%2C%20I%20had%20been%20visiting%20family%20that%20had%20moved%20a%20few%20hours%20north%20of%20Miami%20every%20couple%20of%20months.%20It%20was%20a%20dramatically%20different%20way%20of%20life%20in%20the%20small%20town%20they%20now%20lived%20in%2C%20with%20less%20traffic%20and%20less%20noise.%20I%20caught%20myself%20calculating%20how%20much%20less%20it%20would%20cost%20to%20live%20there%20and%20allowed%20myself%20to%20envision%20a%20different%20way%20of%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20ended%20up%20moving%20over%20the%20summer%20with%20my%20partner%20at%20the%20time%20and%20finding%20a%20house%20to%20rent%20together.%20Just%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20could%20afford%20a%20house%20for%20less%20than%20what%20I%20was%20paying%20for%20a%20on