the%20opportunities%20that%20may%20arise%20from%20this%20tariff%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EROBUST%20INDIA-US%20TIES%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20the%20United%20States%20enjoy%20a%20broad-based%20global%20strategic%20partnership%20covering%20nearly%20every%20major%20domain.%20The%20relationship%20is%20driven%20by%20shared%20democratic%20values%2C%20converging%20strategic%20interests%2C%20and%20dynamic%20people-to-people%20engagement.%20High-level%20exchanges%20continue%20to%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20advancing%20bilateral%20cooperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20nations%20also%20have%20a%20robust%20economic%20partnership.%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Washington%20have%20set%20a%20target%20to%20more%20than%20double%20bilateral%20trade%20to%20%24500%20billion%20by%202030%20from%20the%20current%20over%20%24190%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20nations%20also%20invest%20heavily%20in%20each%20other.%20In%20the%20financial%20year%202023-24%2C%20the%20US%20was%20India's%20third-largest%20source%20of%20FDI%2C%20contributing%20USD%204.99%20billion%20-%20around%209%20per%20cent%20of%20total%20equity%20inflows.%20Indian%20companies%20are%20also%20making%20major%20investments%20in%20the%20US%2C%20with%20a%202023%20CII%20study%20noting%20163%20Indian%20firms%20have%20invested%20over%20USD%2040%20billion%2C%20creating%20425%2C000%20direct%20American%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Csmall%3E%3Cem%3E(Inputs%20from%20Reuters)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744054260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F60m8ccno_jaishankar-rubio_625x300_22_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famid-trump-tariffs-s-jaishankar-us-counterpart-push-for-early-trade-deal-8111548%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20and%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20spoke%20over%20a%20phone%20call%20on%20Monday.%20Both%20le