ck%20and%20smooth%2C%20and%20there%20are%20fewer%20stuttering%20animations%20than%20we%20faced%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsamsung-galaxy-watch-6-classic-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGalaxy%20Watch%206%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Watch%207%20also%20has%2032GB%20of%20storage%2C%20twice%20the%20storage%20as%20the%20previous%20generation%2C%20which%20had%2016GB.%20That's%20great%20news%20if%20you%20like%20to%20store%20music%2C%20podcasts%2C%20audiobooks%2C%20or%20any%20other%20kind%20of%20audio%20on%20your%20smartwatch%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20bring%20your%20phone.%20Indeed%2C%20you%20can%20connect%20your%20Bluetooth%20headphones%20or%20earbuds%20to%20the%20Watch%207%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2229d80ed7-652f-415a-9e96-6df07b38b25c%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Smart%20features%5C%22%3ESmart%20features%3A%20Everything%20you'd%20want%20in%20a%20smartwatch%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Watch%207%20receives%20all%20the%20notifications%20you'd%20want%20from%20your%20phone%20without%20any%20delay%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20unfamiliar%20with%20Samsung's%20Galaxy%20Watches%2C%20you%20have%20to%20manually%20enable%20notifications%20for%20all%20the%20apps%20you%20download%20(best%20done%20through%20the%20Samsung%20Wear%20app%20on%20your%20phone).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20notification%20on%20the%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20Watch%207%2C%20worn%20on%20a%20wrist.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67db1866585f1dff88b29fa4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Watch%207%20performs%20its%20notification%20duties%20well.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20any%20good%20premium%20smartwatch%2C%20you%20can%20make%20and%20take%20calls%2C%20as%20well%20as%20send%20messages%20with%20the%20keyboard%20or%20by%20using%20your%20voice.%20You%20also%20get%20the%20usual%20quick%20replies%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BYes%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BNo.%26quot%3B%20Overall%2C%20the%20Watch%207%20is%20an%20excellent%20companion%20for%20your%20phone%2C%20and%20it's%20especially%20useful%20when%20your%20hands%20are%20busy%20and%20taking%20your%20phone%20out%20is%20inconvenient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20Watch%207%20with%20a%20classic%20blue%20watch%20face%2C%20worn%20on%20a%20wrist.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67db1891b8b41a9673fb21c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20choose%20from%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20watch%20faces%20for%20any%20occasion%2C%20and%20switching%20between%20them%20is%20easy.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20plenty%20of%20watch%20face%20options%20to%20suit%20whatever%20look%20and%20functionality%20you%20want.%20You%20can%20go%20for%20something%20classy%20and%20simple%2C%20or%20use%20a%20watch%20face%20chock-full%20of%20customizable%20complications%20to%20display%20a%20bunch%20of%20information.%20You%20can%20customize%20your%20watch%20face%20from%20the%20Watch%207%20itself%2C%20but%20it's%20easier%20to%20do%20on%20your%20phone.%20However%2C%20you%20can%20quickly%20and%20easily%20switch%20between%20different%20watch%20faces%20you've%20saved%20for%20different%20situations%20straight%20from%20the%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESamsung%20continues%20to%20bolster%20its%20existing%20health%20and%20fitness%20features%20with%20its%20own%20Galaxy%20AI%2C%20like%20fitness%20and%20sleep%20tracking.%20And%20new%20to%20the%20Galaxy%20Watch%207%20is%20the%20AI%20feature%20Energy%20Score%2C%20which%20we%20discuss%20in%20depth%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229ca2f17a-eb0e-4c68-8cc6-17ecdabffe26%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Fitness%20tracking%5C%22%3EFitness%20tracking%3A%20Excellent%20for%20its%20price%2C%20though%20it's%20not%20flawless%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Watch%207%20excels%20as%20a%20fitness%20tracking%20device%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20%24300%20price%20range.%20You%20can%20track%20several%20common%20and%20popular%20workout%20options%2C%20including%20walking%2C%20running%2C%20biking%2C%20track%20run%2C%20hiking%2C%20pool%20swimming%2C%20open%20water%20swimming%2C%20treadmill%2C%20indoor%20biking%2C%20elliptical%20trainer%2C%20circuit%20training%2C%20weight%20machines%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bother%20workout%26quot%3B%20for%20generic%20metrics%20tracking%20if%20your%20specific%20workout%20isn't%20included%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20the%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20Watch%207%20showing%20workout%20options%20on%20the%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67db18c569253ccddf99bb61%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Watch%207%20can%20track%20a%20variety%20of%20common%20and%20popular%20workouts%20and%20your%20metrics%20for%20any%20sport%20or%20activity%20that%20it%20doesn't%20specifically%20include.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Watch%207%20connected%20to%20GPS%20in%20about%20five%20seconds%20without%20a%20connection%20to%20its%20companion%20phone%20or%20WiFi%2C%20which%20is%20pretty%20quick.%20Accuracy%20is%20good%2C%20but%20like%20many%20smartwatches%20in%20the%20%24300%20price%20range%2C%20it's%20not%20without%20fault.%20While%20I%20don't%20expect%20it%20to%20know%20what%20side%20of%20a%20narrow%20two-lane%20road%20I'm%20on%2C%20it%20can%20be%20thwarted%20by%20heavy%20tree%20cover%20or%20tall%20buildings%2C%20where%20it%20might%20show%20random%20loop-de-loops%20or%20slight%20deviations%20in%20my%20walking%20or%20running%20path.%20That's%20no%20big%20deal%20for%20most%20people%2C%20but%20I%20can%20picture%20fitness%20enthusiasts%20seeking%20something%20more%20accurate%2C%20like%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-fitness-tracker%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20fitness%20trackers%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20have%20extra%20components%20for%20better%20GPS%20accuracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Watch%207%20features%20handy%20auto-workout%20detection%20that%20turns%20on%20after%2010%20minutes%20of%20activity%20if%20you%20forget%20to%20start%20a%20workout.%20It's%20limited%20to%20walking%2C%20running%2C%20biking%2C%20elliptical%20trainer%2C%20rowing%20machine%2C%20pool%20swim%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bdynamic%20workout%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20Samsung%20says%20are%20%26quot%3Bhigh-movement%20activities.%26quot%3B%20You%20can%20pick%20which%20workouts%20you'd%20want%20to%20auto-detect%20and%20even%20set%20the%20times%20and%20days%20of%20the%20week%20for%20auto-workout%20detection%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2296af5c14-205f-4daf-b61d-5bf445db71c9%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Health%20features%5C%22%3EHealth%20features%3A%20Remarkable%20data%20tracking%20and%20value%20with%20an%20upgraded%20sensor%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20BioActive%20sensor%20on%20the%20underside%20of%20the%20Galaxy%20Watch%207%2C%20held%20in%20a%20hand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67db1a5eb8b41a9673fb2219%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Watch%207%20has%20exceptional%20health%20features%2C%20though%20some%20are%20locked%20to%20Samsung%20phone%20users.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Watch%207%20is%20brimming%20with%20health%20tracking%20and%20monitoring%20features%20powered%20by%20its%20upgraded%20BioActive%20sensor%2C%20from%20basic%20heart%20rate%20and%20step%20measuring%20to%20advanced%20sleep%20tracking%2C%20electrocardiogram%20(ECG)%2C%20and%20body%20composition%20readings.%20The%20Watch%207's%20sensors%20contribute%20to%20your%20health%20profile%20in%20the%20Samsung%20Health%20app%2C%20which%20includes%20an%20Energy%20Score%2C%20daily%20activity%2C%20sleep%20analyzer%2C%20workout%20summaries%2C%20menstrual%20cycle%20tracking%2C%20AGEs%20(metabolic%20health)%20index%2C%20blood%20oxygen%2C%20and%20stress%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnergy%20Score%20is%20an%20AI-powered%20health%20feature%20designed%20to%20give%20you%20an%20idea%20of%20your%20energy%20levels%20for%20the%20day%20with%20a%20score%20out%20of%20100%2C%20and%20it's%20based%20on%20your%20previous%20night's%20sleep%20quality%20and%20previous%20day's%20activity.%20If%20your%20score%20is%20low%2C%20the%20Samsung%20Health%20app%20will%20make%20recommendations%2C%20like%20reducing%20activity%20to%20recover%20or%20sleeping%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20not%20especially%20active%2C%20Energy%20Score%20isn't%20particularly%20useful.%20I%20can%20tell%20pretty%20easily%20if%20my%20energy%20levels%20are%20low%20and%20come%20to%20my%20own%20conclusion%20that%20I%20need%20to%20take%20it%20easier%20or%20go%20to%20bed%20earlier%20that%20day%2C%20if%20possible.%20It's%20a%20bit%20like%20looking%20at%20a%20weather%20app%20to%20check%20if%20it's%20raining%20when%20you%20can%20look%20out%20the%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20series%20of%20screenshots%20from%20Samsung's%20Galaxy%20Z%20Flip%206%20showing%20Samsung's%20AI-driven%20Energy%20Score%20feature%20with%20readings%20taken%20from%20the%20Galaxy%20Watch%207.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67db18f6585f1dff88b29fcb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEnergy%20Score%20gives%20you%20an%20idea%20of%20your%20physical%20and%20mental%20readiness%20for%20the%20day%20based%20on%20your%20previous%20night's%20sleep%20and%20previous%20day's%20activity%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20find%20it%20that%20useful.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20if%20you're%20active%20and%20working%20regularly%2C%20Energy%20Score%20can%20prove%20useful%20by%20recommending%20how%20long%20to%20rest%20(measured%20in%20days)%20before%20you%20should%20engage%20in%20your%20next%20major%20activity%20or%20workout.%20Rest%20days%20may%20be%20common%20knowledge%20for%20anyone%20working%20out%2C%20but%20Energy%20Score%20can%20give%20you%20recommendations%20based%20on%20your%20own%20data%20and%20metrics%20rather%20than%20a%20general%20recommendation%20based%20on%20the%20average%20person%20who%20engaged%20in%20the%20average%20workout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20body%20composition%20feature%20has%20existed%20since%20the%20Galaxy%20Watch%204%20series%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20an%20interesting%20feature%20I%20don't%20see%20on%20other%20smartwatches.%20While%20it's%20not%20designed%20to%20replace%20a%20body%20composition%20reading%20from%20a%20medical%20professional%2C%20it%20can%20give%20you%20a%20general%20idea%20of%20your%20body%20mass%20index%20(BMI)%2C%20skeletal%20muscle%2C%20fat%20mass%2C%20body%20water%2C%20body%20fat%20percentage%2C%20and%20basal%20metabolic%20rate%20(BMR).%20In%20turn%2C%20it%20can%20give%20you%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20(compared%20to%20simple%20weight%20loss)%20of%20how%20your%20body%20is%20changing%2C%20whether%20you're%20working%20out%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20showing%20the%20awkward%20process%20of%20taking%20a%20body%20composition%20reading%20on%20the%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20Watch%207.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67db192fb8b41a9673fb21df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBody%20composition%20reading%20with%20the%20Watch%207%20is%20an%20awkward%20affair%20that%20doesn't%