%20pm%20India%20time).%20Citing%20his%20earlier%20%26quot%3Bwarning%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Btariff%20abuser%26quot%3B%20China%2C%20he%20shared%20a%20post%20on%20his%20social%20media%20platform%20Truth%20Social%2C%20in%20which%20he%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BYesterday%2C%20China%20issued%20retaliatory%20tariffs%20of%2034%20per%20cent%2C%20on%20top%20of%20their%20already%20record%20setting%20tariffs%2C%20non-monetary%20tariffs%2C%20illegal%20subsidization%20of%20companies%2C%20and%20massive%20long%20term%20currency%20manipulation%2C%20despite%20my%20warning%20that%20any%20country%20that%20retaliates%20against%20the%20US%20by%20issuing%20additional%20tariffs%2C%20above%20and%20beyond%20their%20already%20existing%20long%20term%20tariff%20abuse%20of%20our%20nation%2C%20will%20be%20immediately%20met%20with%20new%20and%20substantially%20higher%20tariffs%2C%20over%20and%20above%20those%20initially%20set.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20warn%20that%20%26quot%3BIf%20China%20does%20not%20withdraw%20its%2034%20per%20cent%20increase%20above%20their%20already%20long%20term%20trading%20abuses%20by%20tomorrow%2C%20April%208th%2C%202025%2C%20the%20United%20States%20will%20impose%20additional%20tariffs%20on%20China%20of%2050%20per%20cent%2C%20effective%20April%209th.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2F114297331052690348%2Fembed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20furious%20US%20president%20also%20threatened%20the%20end%20all%20talks%20with%20China%20regarding%20Beijing's%20request%20for%20dialogue%20amid%20a%20globally%20spiralling%20tariff%20war.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20nations%20that%20have%20not%20retaliated%20the%20US%20import%20duty%2C%20will%20be%20given%20a%20chance%20to%20negotiate.%C2%A0%26quot%3BAdditionally%2C%20all%20talks%20with%20China%20concerning%20their%20requested%20meetings%20with%20us