et%20to%20discuss%20Gaza%2C%20where%20a%20short-lived%20US-brokered%20truce%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20has%20collapsed%2C%20and%20growing%20tensions%20with%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20greeted%20Netanyahu%20outside%20the%20West%20Wing%20and%20pumped%20his%20fist%2C%20before%20the%20two%20leaders%20--%20both%20wearing%20dark%20suits%2C%20red%20ties%20and%20white%20shirts%20--%20went%20inside%20for%20a%20meeting%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20planned%20press%20conference%20between%20the%20two%20leaders%20was%20canceled%20at%20short%20notice%20without%20explanation%20in%20an%20unusual%20move.%20During%20his%20last%20visit%2C%20Netanyahu%20and%20Trump%20both%20spoke%20to%20reporters%20in%20the%20Oval%20and%20then%20held%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20premier's%20visit%20is%20his%20second%20to%20Trump%20since%20the%20US%20president%20returned%20to%20power%20and%20comes%20at%20short%20notice%20--%20just%20days%20after%20Trump%20slapped%20a%2017%20percent%20tariff%20on%20Israel%20in%20his%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20announcement%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20refused%20to%20exempt%20the%20top%20beneficiary%20of%20US%20military%20aid%20from%20his%20global%20tariff%20salvo%20as%20he%20said%20Washington%20had%20a%20significant%20trade%20deficit%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20said%20on%20his%20way%20to%20Washington%20on%20Sunday%20that%20they%20would%20discuss%20%26quot%3Bthe%20hostages%2C%20achieving%20victory%20in%20Gaza%2C%20and%20of%20course%20the%20tariff%20regime%20that%20has%20also%20been%20imposed%20on%20Israel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20the%20first%20international%20leader%2C%20the%20first%20foreign%20leader%20who%20will%20meet%20with%20President%20Trump%20on%20a%20matter%20so%20crucial%20to%20Israel's%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20video%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20long%20line%20of%20leaders%20who%20want%20to%20do%20this.%20I%20believe%20this%20reflects%20the%20special%20personal%20relationship%20and%20the%20unique%20bond%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Israel%2C%20which%20is%20so%20vital%20at%20this%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20met%20with%20US%20Commerce%20Secretary%20Howard%20Lutnick%20and%20US%20Trade%20Representative%20Jamieson%20Greer%20on%20Sunday%20night%20soon%20after%20his%20arrival%2C%20according%20to%20his%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20premier%20also%20met%20Trump's%20special%20Middle%20East%20envoy%20Steve%20Witkoff%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20told%20reporters%20on%20Sunday%20that%20%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20talk%20about%20trade%2C%20and%20we're%20going%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20obvious%20subject.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20going%20on%20with%20the%20Middle%20East%20right%20now%20that%20have%20to%20be%20silenced%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttack%20on%20paramedics%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20sparked%20by%20Hamas's%20October%202023%20attack%2C%20and%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20Israeli%20and%20US%20hostages%20still%20held%20in%20Gaza%20will%20be%20a%20major%20subject%20of%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20resumed%20intense%20strikes%20on%20Gaza%20on%20March%2018%2C%20and%20the%20weeks-long%20ceasefire%20with%20Hamas%20that%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Egypt%20and%20Qatar%20had%20brokered%20collapsed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20so%20far%20backed%20Israel%20to%20the%20hilt%2C%20accusing%20Hamas%20of%20failing%20to%20release%20the%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20has%20also%20brushed%20off%20an%20incident%20in%20which%2015%20medics%20and%20rescuers%20were%20killed%20by%20Israeli%20forces%20last%20month%20in%20Gaza%2C%20sparking%20international%20condemnation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20army%20chief%20on%20Monday%20ordered%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeeper%26quot%