e%20same%20time%20as%20the%20US%20stock%20market%20boom%20of%201981-82%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fhow-a-long-stock-market-boom-has-doomed-india-s-america-s-competitiveness-125040700786_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Twenty%20Years%20On%2C%20This%20US%20Couple's%20Disappearance%20Is%20Still%20A%20Mystery%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwenty%20years%20ago%2C%20on%20a%20Saturday%20night%2C%20Richard%20Petrone%20Jr%20and%20his%20girlfriend%20Danielle%20Imbo%2C%20accompanied%20by%20their%20friends%2C%20went%20out%20to%20a%20bar%20in%20Philadelphia.%20Once%20the%20outing%20was%20over%2C%20Mr%20Petrone%20Jr%20was%20supposed%20to%20drop%20Ms%20Imbo%20off%20at%20her%20home%20in%20New%20Jersey%20and%20head%20back%20to%20his%20apartment%20in%20Philadelphia.%20Their%20friends%20or%20anyone%20else%20never%20heard%20back%20from%20them%20after%20they%20left%20the%20bar%2C%20CNN%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigators%20found%20no%20forensic%20evidence%20of%20the%20couple's%20whereabouts%20after%20they%20were%20last%20seen%20at%20the%20bar%2C%20retired%20FBI%20special%20agent%20Vito%20Roselli%2C%20who%20was%20the%20case's%20first%20lead%20investigator%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20truck%20was%20not%20spotted%20on%20any%20of%20the%20area's%20toll%20bridge%20cameras%20and%20the%20couple's%20credit%20cards%20and%20bank%20accounts%20registered%20no%20activity%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%2C%20along%20with%20Mr%20Petrone%20Jr's%202001%20black%20Dodge%20Dakota%20pick-up%20truck%2C%20just%20disappeared%20into%20the%20night.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20mother%20Marge%20Petrone%20said%20she%20knew%20something%20was%20wrong%20when%20she%20didn't%20immediately%20hear%20back%20from%20him.%20%26quot%3BHis%20phone%20was%20never%20off%20-%20it%20was%20always%20in%20his%20hands%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2025%2F04%2F06%2Fus%2Fpetrone-imbo-missing-philadelphia-cec%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20day%2C%20there%20are%20no%20leads%20in%20the%20case.%20No%20one%20in%20the%20family%20thinks%20the%20couple%20planned%20their%20disappearance%20and%20relocated%20to%20a%20different%20area%20to%20start%20a%20new%20life.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20they%20were%20parents%20to%20a%20teen%20and%20a%20toddler%2C%20respectively.%20According%20to%20their%20families%2C%20they%20would%20never%20just%20abandon%20their%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Roselli%2C%20who%20now%20works%20in%20cybersecurity%20for%20an%20international%20company%20in%20Miami%2C%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20stays%20with%20me.%20Like%2C%20'What%20did%20I%20miss%3F'%20...%20is%20constantly%20living%20rent-free%20in%20my%20head.%20But%20also%20because%20you%20want%20to%20see%20closure%20for%20the%20two%20families.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFBI's%20Philadelphia%20office%20says%20the%20matter%20remains%20a%20top%20priority.%20According%20to%20one%20of%20the%20statements%2C%20following%20the%20couple's%20disappearance%2C%20the%20FBI%20collaborated%20with%20law%20enforcement%20from%20other%20jurisdictions%20in%20New%20York%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20and%20Pennsylvania.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20dispatched%20divers%20to%20investigate%20the%20Delaware%20River%20and%20other%20bodies%20of%20water%20between%20Philadelphia%20and%20Mount%20Laurel.%20Investigators%20followed%20leads%20in%20many%20states%20and%20examined%20financial%2C%20phone%2C%20and%20road%20toll%20data.%20They%20also%20looked%20into%20a%20flurry%20of%20theories%2C%20but%20nothing%20brought%20any%20fruitful%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETechnology%20was%20less%20developed%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20than%20it%20is%20now%2C%20which%20limited%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20investigation.%20While%