3B%20Kalavathi%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20parent%20said%20he%20appealed%20to%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20to%20consider%20rescheduling%20the%20exam%20for%20the%20affected%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20release%2C%20the%20All%20India%20Students'%20Federation%20(AISF)%20blamed%20the%20officials%20for%20inefficient%20traffic%20management%20during%20exam%20hours.%20The%20students%20had%20missed%20the%20opportunity%20to%20write%20the%20exam%20through%20no%20fault%20of%20their%20own%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarthik%20Yellapragada%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20opposition%20YSR%20Congress%2C%20said%20the%20state%20%26quot%3Bdeserves%20a%20better%20science%20and%20technology%20minister%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20actor-politician%2C%20true%20to%20his%20cinematic%20image%2C%20continues%20to%20treat%20public%20office%20like%20a%20press%20release%20event...%20It%20is%20time%20that%20we%20stop%20clapping%20to%20cinematic%20moments%20and%20start%20demanding%20real%20accountability%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%20in%20a%20video%20message.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20has%20contacted%20Pawan%20Kalyan's%20office%20but%20has%20received%20no%20response.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20the%20city%20police%20claimed%20the%20students%20were%20expected%20to%20reach%20the%20exam%20centres%20by%207%20am%20and%20had%20these%2030%20students%20been%20on%20time%2C%20there%20was%20no%20question%20of%20their%20being%20held%20up%20by%20traffic.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BAs%20per%20the%20admit%20card%20of%20the%20above-mentioned%20examinations%2C%20every%20candidate%20has%20to%20report%20at%2007%3A00%20am%20and%20the%20gate%20of%20the%20examination%20centre%20will%20be%20closed%20at%208%3A30%20am%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20rough%20translation%20of%20their%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Deputy%20Chief%20minister%2C%20the%20police%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bpassed%20through%20the%20said%20junction%20at%208%3A41%20am%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20movement%20of%20the%20Deputy%20CM%20through%20that%20area%20at%208%3A41%20AM%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20late%20arrival%20of%20the%20students%20who%20were%20supposed%20to%20report%20at%207%20am%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20read.%3Cbr%3E%5CnTraffic%20on%20the%20BRTS%20Road%20and%20Gopalapatnam-Pendurthi%20Service%20Road%20has%20not%20been%20stopped%20till%208%3A30%20am%20to%20ensure%20free%20movement%20of%20the%20candidates%20to%20the%20exam%20centre%2C%20the%20police%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoreover%2C%20since%20the%20commencement%20of%20these%20examinations%20on%20April%202%2C%20if%20we%20look%20at%20the%20first%20shift%20on%20each%20examination%20day%2C%20the%20number%20of%20absent%20candidates%20(including%20latecomers)%20at%20the%20centre%20was%2081%2C%2065%2C%2076%20and%2061%2C%20which%20means%20that%20the%20number%20of%20absent%20students%20(including%20latecomers)%20is%20less%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744045620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fhu9qn88_pawan-kalyan-convoy_625x300_07_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstudents-say-missed-exam-due-to-pawan-kalyans-convoy-cops-reject-claim-8110744%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thirty%20students%20in%20Visakhapatnam%20could%20not%20reach%20their%20exam%20centre%20and%20failed%20to%20take%20the%20engineering%20entrance%20exam%2C%20apparently%20after%20being%20delayed%20by%20the%20convoy%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Pawan%20Kalyan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstudents-say-missed-exam-due-to-pawan-kalyans-convoy-cops-reject-claim-8110744%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alia%20