20Oil%20dipped%20further%20-%20nearly%20reaching%20%2450%20per%20barrel%20as%20the%20oil%20markets%20faced%20extreme%20turbulence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20-%20Donald%20Trump's%20reciprocal%20tariffs%2C%20which%20have%20sent%20global%20markets%2C%20including%20that%20of%20oil%2C%20into%20a%20free%20fall.%20To%20add%20to%20the%20misery%2C%20China%2C%20the%20world's%20second-largest%20economy%2C%20also%20announced%20retaliatory%20measures%20to%20target%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20oil%20and%20gas%20sector%20is%20the%20largest%20contributor%20of%20cash%20flow%20in%20the%20Russian%20federal%20budget.%20In%20March%20alone%2C%20the%20revenue%20from%20the%20key%20sector%20fell%20by%20more%20than%2017%20per%20cent%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20month%20a%20year%20ago.%20This%20is%20before%20April's%20unending%20downward%20spiral%20after%20Trump's%20tariff%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20falling%20oil%20prices%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20the%20Russian%20economy%2C%20Kremlin%20spokesman%20Dmitry%20Peskov%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%20this%20indicator%20is%20very%20important%20for%20filling%20the%20budget.%20Our%20authorities%20are%20very%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20situation%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20extremely%20turbulent%2C%20tense%2C%20and%20emotionally%20charged.%20We%20aim%20to%20take%20measures%20in%20order%20to%20minimise%20the%20consequences%20of%20this%20economic%20storm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20Bloomberg%20report%2C%20on%20Friday%2C%20Russia's%20Urals%20oil%20was%20trading%20at%20a%20low%20of%20%2452%20per%20barrel%20at%20Primorsk%2C%20a%20port%20in%20the%20Baltic%20Sea%20.%20It%20fell%20even%20further%20on%20Monday%2C%20inching%20its%20way%20towards%20the%20%2450%20per%20barrel%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrillions%20of%20dollars%20have%20been%20lost%20across%20global%20markets%20in%20under%2072%20hours%20and%20investors%20are%20seriously%20concerned%20of%20a%20possible%20recession%20in%20the%20making.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWTI%20Crude%20or%20Texas%20crude%2C%20which%20is%20the%20US%20benchmark%20for%20American%20oil%2C%20is%20also%20at%20a%20low%20of%20%2460%20per%20barrel%2C%20while%20the%20Brent%20Crude%20prices%20internationally%20fell%20to%20%2464%20per%20barrel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20President%20Trump%20doubled%20down%20on%20his%20stance%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BOil%20prices%20are%20down...there%20is%20no%20Inflation%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20outrightly%20rejected%20economists'%20concerns%20of%20a%20possible%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20his%20social%20media%20platform%20Truth%20Social%2C%20President%20Trump%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BOil%20prices%20are%20down%2C%20interest%20rates%20are%20down%20(the%20slow%20moving%20Fed%20should%20cut%20rates!)%2C%20food%20prices%20are%20down%2C%20there%20is%20NO%20INFLATION%2C%20and%20the%20long%20time%20abused%20USA%20is%20bringing%20in%20Billions%20of%20Dollars%20a%20week%20from%20the%20abusing%20countries%20on%20Tariffs%20that%20are%20already%20in%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20singled%20out%20China%2C%20saying%20it%20is%20them%20who%20really%20are%20to%20blame%2C%20along%20with%20past%20leaders%20in%20the%20US%2C%20who%20%26quot%3Ballowed%20for%20this%20to%20happen%26quot%3B.%20On%20Truth%20Social%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20biggest%20abuser%20of%20them%20all%2C%20China%2C%20whose%20markets%20are%20crashing%2C%20just%20raised%20its%20Tariffs%20by%2034%25%2C%20on%20top%20of%20its%20long%20term%20ridiculously%20high%20Tariffs%20(Plus!)%2C%20not%20acknowledging%20my%20warning%20for%20abusing%20countries%20not%20to%20retaliate.%20They've%20made%20enough%2C%20for%20decades%2C%20taking%20advantage%20of%20the%20Good%20OL'%20USA!%20Our%20past%20%26quot%3Bleaders%26quot%3B%20are%20to%20blame%20for%20allowing%20this%2C%20and%20so%20much%20else%2C%20to%20happen%20to%20our%20Country.%20MAKE%20AMERICA%20GREAT%20AGAIN!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2F114296287858068040%2Fembed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%2C%20had%20on%20Wednesday%20(US%20time-zone)%2C%20announced%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20on%20nations%20that%20tariff%20the%20US%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20a%2010%20per%20cent%20tariff%20on%20the%20entire%20world.%20Since%20then%20global%20stock%20markets%20are%20experiencing%20an%20irrecoverable%20free%20fall%2C%20as%20are%20the%20oil%20or%20crude%20markets%2C%20as%20well%20as%20commodities%20markets.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744044720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F6sb9v2b8_trump-putin-oil-prices-reuters_625x300_07_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fextremely-turbulent-russian-oil-market-rattled-by-trump-tariff-fallout-8109931%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%2C%20whose%20economy%20is%20heavily%20dependent%20on%20oil%2C%20energy%2C%20and%20mineral%20exports%20to%20the%20world%2C%20is%20staring%20at%20a%20crisis%2C%20should%20oil%20prices%20continue%20to%20plummet%20the%20way%20they%20are%20currently.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fextremely-turbulent-russian-oil-market-rattled-by-trump-tariff-fallout-8109931%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tahawwur%20Rana's%20Last%20Plea%20Against%20Extradition%20To%20India%20Rejected%20By%20US%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20denied%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20terror%20attack%20accused%20Tahawwur%20Rana's%20last%20application%20seeking%20a%20stay%20on%20his%20extradition%20to%20India%2C%C2%A0moving%20him%20closer%20to%20being%20handed%20over%20to%20Indian%20authorities%20to%20face%20jus