S.%20tariffs%20in%20the%20name%20of%20reciprocity%20only%20serve%20its%20own%20interest%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinutes%20before%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20opened%20amid%20a%20worldwide%20selloff%2C%20in%20a%20separate%20post%2C%20he%20also%20asked%20Americans%20to%20%26quot%3Bbe%20strong%2C%20courageous%2C%20and%20patient%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20has%20a%20chance%20to%20do%20something%20that%20should%20have%20been%20done%20DECADES%20AGO%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20in%20reference%20to%20his%20tariff%20reforms%20that%20have%20upended%20the%20global%20economy.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20be%20Weak!%20Don't%20be%20Stupid!...%20Be%20Strong%2C%20Courageous%2C%20and%20Patient%2C%20and%20GREATNESS%20will%20be%20the%20result!%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWall%20Street%20was%20not%20untouched%20by%20the%20global%20stock%20market%20decline.%C2%A0All%20three%20major%20US%20indices%20were%20down%20more%20than%20three%20percent%20in%20early%20trading.%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20opened%203.2%20per%20cent%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThey%20Played%20It%20Wrong%2C%20Panicked%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthey-played-it-wrong-they-panicked-trump-on-china-imposing-34-tariff-on-us-goods-8087750%5C%22%3EAfter%20China%20announced%20retaliatory%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20sparked%20a%20trade%20war%20between%20Beijing%20and%20Washington%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BChina%20played%20it%20wrong%2C%20they%20panicked%20--%20the%20one%20thing%20they%20cannot%20afford%20to%20do!%26quot%3B%20in%20full%20caps%2C%20his%20trademark%20style%20of%20writing%20on%20social%20media%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump%2C%20who%20is%20a%20real%20estate%20mogul%20and%20a%20billionaire%20businessman%2C%20is%20relying%20on%20the%20theory%20that%20it%20would%20force%20countries%20to%20re-negotiate%20trade%20deals%20and%20bring%20fore