20of%20being%20a%20fraud.%20Nearly%20two%20decades%20later%2C%20the%20same%20name%20has%20resurfaced%20-%20this%20time%20in%20Damoh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20known%20to%20his%20patients%20as%20Dr%20N%20John%20Camm.%20supposedly%20a%20UK-returned%20cardiologist%2C%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20resident%20of%20Dehradun%20with%20an%20unverifiable%20past%2C%20questionable%20degrees%2C%20and%20no%20cardiology%20registration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%2C%20he%20was%20performing%20complex%20procedures%20at%20Damoh's%20Mission%20Hospital%2C%20including%20angiographies%20and%20anioplasties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20his%20Aadhaar%20card%20says%20his%20real%20name%20Narendra%20Vikramaditya%20Yadav.%20His%20qualifications%20--%20an%20MBBS%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20followed%20by%20multiple%20dubious%20MD%20and%20cardiology%20degrees%20from%20places%20as%20varied%20as%20Darjeeling%2C%20Calcutta%2C%20and%20the%20UK-none%20carrying%20verifiable%20registration%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20was%20hired%20through%20a%20placement%20agency%20and%20began%20treating%20heart%20patients%20under%20a%20fake%20identity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20local%20authorities%2C%20he%20carried%20out%2015%20operations%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%20seven%20patients.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victims%20include%20Rahisa%20Begum%2C%20Mangal%20Singh%2C%20Budha%20Ahirwal%2C%20Israel%20Khan%2C%20and%20Dasonda%20Raikwar%2C%20All%20died%20within%20hours%20of%20undergoing%20procedures%20allegedly%20conducted%20by%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gravity%20of%20the%20scandal%20surfaced%20when%20families%20of%20victims%20like%20Rahisa%20Begum%20and%20Mangal%20Singh%20came%20forward.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahisa%2C%20who%20had%20chest%20pain%20on%20January%2012%2C%20underwent%20surgery%20three%20days%20later%20and%20died%20within%20hours.%20%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20my%20mother%20died%2C%20the%20doctor%20vanished%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20her%20son%2C%20Nabi%20Qureshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangal%20Singh%2C%20brought%20in%20with%20gastric%20complaints%2C%20was%20also%20operated%20on%20and%20died%20the%20same%20day.%20%26quot%3BThey%20didn't%20even%20give%20the%20injection%20they%20had%20ordered.%20When%20we%20demanded%20a%20postmortem%20examination%2C%20the%20hospital%20insisted%20it%20wasn't%20necessary%20and%20handed%20us%20the%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20alleged%20his%20son%2C%20Jitendra%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20the%20families%20claim%20they%20were%20not%20even%20shown%20the%20prescribed%20injections%20or%20medicines.%20In%20others%2C%20the%20hospital%20insisted%20on%20skipping%20postmortems.%20The%20logic%20--%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20the%20point%20now%3F%20The%20operation%20is%20done%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20a%20case%20has%20been%20registered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20Tiwari%2C%20CSP%2C%20Damoh%2C%20said%20%26quot%3BCHMO%20(Chief%20Medical%20and%20Health%20Officer)%20Dr%20MK%20Jain%20has%20submitted%20a%20report%20stating%20that%20Dr.%20Narendra%20John%20Kem%2C%20employed%20at%20Mission%20Hospital%2C%20presented%20forged%20and%20fraudulent%20medical%20documents.%20The%20license%20he%20claimed%20to%20hold%20for%20medical%20practice%20was%20not%20registered.%20Investigations%20have%20revealed%20that%20he%20conducted%20angiographies%20and%20angioplasties%20without%20proper%20qualifications.%20Based%20on%20the%20findings%20and%20the%20suspicious%20nature%20of%20his%20documents%2C%20we%20have%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20him%20for%20forgery%2C%20fraud%2C%20and%20use%20of%20fabricated%20documents%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPushpa%20Khare%2C%20In-Charge%20Manager%2C%20Mission%20Hospital%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BDr.%20Narendra%20was%20appointed%20through%20IWUS%2C%20an%20agency%20registered%20with%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government.%20We%20had%20a%20contract%20with%20the%20company%2C%20under%20which%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20his%20monthly%20salary%20was%20to%20be%20paid%20to%20them%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%2C%20she%20said%2C%20was%20responsible%20for%20verifying%20the%20doctor's%20credentials%20and%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDr%20Narendra%20also%20took%20away%20our%20portable%20echo%20machine%2C%20worth%20around%205%20to%207%20lakh%20rupees.%20We%20have%20filed%20a%20complaint%20regarding%20the%20theft%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEchoes%20of%202006%3A%20When%20a%20Speaker%20Died%20Under%20His%20Knife%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20Narendra%20Yadav's%20first%20brush%20with%20controversy.%20In%202006%2C%20he%20was%20named%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20death%20of%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20Shukla%2C%20then%20Speaker%20of%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20Assembly%2C%20who%20died%20during%20a%20surgery%20in%20Bilaspur's%20Apollo%20Hospital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Yadav%20was%20passed%20off%20as%20a%20reputed%20UK-based%20doctor.%20An%20inquiry%20was%20ordered%20then%2C%20but%20no%20lasting%20action%20followed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20with%20new%20deaths%20linked%20to%20him%2C%20questions%20are%20being%20raised%3A%20Why%20wasn't%20he%20blacklisted%3F%20How%20was%20he%20allowed%20to%20practice%20again%3F%3Cbr%3E%5CnJustice%20(Retd.)%20Anil%20Shukla%2C%20a%20family%20member%20of%20the%20late%20Speaker%2C%20said%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20found%20out%20even%20back%20then%20that%20he%20was%20not%20qualified.%20If%20the%20system%20had%20acted%20then%2C%20so%20many%20innocent%20lives%20could%20have%20been%20saved%20today%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20father%20underwent%20surgery%2C%20and%20I%20was%20present%20at%20the%20time.%20I%20grew%20suspicious%20when%20the%20catheter%20had%20to%20be%20repeatedly%20inserted.%20Later%2C%20others%20also%20told%20us%20the%20doctor%20was%20a%20fraud.%20But%20Apollo%20Hospital%20introduced%20him%20as%20a%20'London-returned'%20expert%20and%20praised%20him%20so%20much%20that%20we%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20believe.%20Now%2C%20the%20government%20must%20take%20suo%20motu%20cognizance%20of%20this%20and%20order%20an%20inquiry%20by%20a%20sitting%20High%20Court%20judge%20so%20that%20justice%20can%20be%20served%20to%20the%20victims%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Pramod%20Tiwari%2C%20CMHO%2C%20Bilaspur%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20sent%20a%20team%20to%20investigate%20the%20matter%20and%20called%20for%20all%20documents.%20If%20he%20was%20practicing%20without%20proper%20registration%2C%20it%20is%20a%20very%20serious%20matter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevesh%20Gopal%2C%20an%20executive%20from%20Apollo%20Bilaspur%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20very%20old%20case%2C%20around%2018%20to%2019%20years%20old.%20We%20will%20only%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20details%20after%20verifying%20the%20relevant%20documents.%20What%20steps%20were%20taken%20at%20that%20time%20will%20become%20clear%20after%20reviewing%20the%20paperwork.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Mohan%20Yadav%20said%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20all%20those%20found%20responsible.%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20will%20be%20spared%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744037040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F8qp58j2o_fake-doctor-madhya-pradesh_625x300_07_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-damoh-fake-doctor-was-linked-to-ex-chhattisgarh-speakers-death-during-surgery-8109747%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20fake%20doctor%20who%20operated%20on%20a%20former%20Speaker%20of%20Chhattisgarh-an%20operation%20that%20led%20to%20his%20death%20--%20has%20been%20in%20active%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-damoh-fake-doctor-was-linked-to-