20in%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Gaya%20and%20Nalanda%2C%20and%20saw%20over%20700%20women%20leaders%20become%20stakeholders%20in%20the%20cause%2C%20joining%20in%20solar-related%20discussions.%20In%20another%20successful%20example%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F268152%2Fmaharashtra-village-manyachiwadi-solar-gram-electricity-sustainable-women-success%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Manyachiwadi%20village%20%3C%2Fa%3Eadvocates%20for%20a%20similar%20model.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20village%20set%20a%20precedent%20becoming%20the%20first%20in%20Maharashtra%20to%20be%20100%20percent%20electrified%20by%20solar.%20Almost%20two%20decades%20ago%2C%20when%20conventional%20energy%20was%20reigning%20the%20scene%2C%20Manyachiwadi%20subverted%20the%20trend%20by%20transitioning%20to%20solar.%20They%20started%20small.%20The%20women%20of%20the%20village%20began%20pooling%20in%20Rs%20100%20every%20month%20until%20the%20sum%20was%20enough%20to%20install%20solar%20systems%20in%20their%20homes.%20Today%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20pay%20a%20rupee%20for%20electricity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20world%20beyond%20the%20panels%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERooftop%20solar%20and%20microgrids%20are%20fantastic.%20But%2C%20while%20advocating%20for%20these%2C%20entrepreneurs%20see%20potential%20in%20solar%20devices%20such%20as%20solar%20dryers%2C%20biogas%20grids%20and%20water%20pumps.%20These%20are%20a%20great%20way%20to%20ease%20villages%20into%20the%20world%20of%20renewable%20energy.%20And%20once%20they%20see%20how%20lucrative%20solar%20is%2C%20it%20might%20convince%20them%20to%20invest%20in%20panels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELatika%20Patil%20from%20Dahanu%2C%20Maharashtra%20is%20one%20example.%20She%20belongs%20to%20a%20family%20that%20has%20been%20cultivating%20chickoo%20for%20around%2050%20years.%20But%20the%20harvest%20would%20spoil%20when%20there%20weren%E2%80%99t%20as%20many%20buyers.%20After%20her%20retirement%20in%202015%2C%20Latika%20took%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20the%20processing%20of%20fruits.%20At%20first%2C%20she%20resorted%20to%20sun-drying%20them%20but%20soon%20stumbled%20upon%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F282854%2Fmaharashtra-family-solar-drying-machine-food-processing-chikoo-increases-sales%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20conduction%20dryer%20(SCD)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20latter%20was%20more%20favourable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsolar-4-1743772472.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Solar%20conduction%20dryers%20are%20incredibly%20beneficial%20in%20fruit%20processing%20and%20result%20in%20greater%20turnover%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsolar-4-1743772472.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsolar-4-1743772472-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsolar-4-1743772472-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsolar-4-1743772472-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsolar-4-1743772472-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418048%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESolar%20conduction%20dryers%20are%20incredibly%20beneficial%20in%20fruit%20processing%20and%20result%20in%20greater%20turnover%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Latika%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20any%20climatic%20circumstances%2C%20the%20temperature%20of%20these%20plates%20%5Bof%20the%20SCD%5D%20is%20maintained%20at%2055-60%20degrees%2C%20which%20helps%20in%20conserving%20the%20nutrients%2C%20thus%20preventing%20the%20natural%20sugar%20content%20in%20the%20fruit%20from%20caramelising%20to%20form%20a%20dark%20colour%2C%E2%80%9D%20her%20son%20Ninad%20says.%20This%20method%20also%20extends%20the%20shelf-life%20of%20the%20fruits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20solar%20dryers%20are%20one%20accessory%2C%20solar%20water%20pumps%20are%20another.%20Shweta%20of%20ONergy%20points%20to%20how%20farmers%20have%20been%20seeing%20higher%20crop%20yields%20and%20reduced%20irrigation%20costs%20through%20the%20ONergy%20solar%20water%20pumps.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20allows%20them%20to%20be%20less%20dependent%20on%20expensive%20diesel-powered%20pumps.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20increased%20profits%20and%20sustainable%20farming%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Gram%20Oorja%20wields%20its%20biogas%20cooking%20grids%20as%20one%20of%20its%20most%20remarkable%20innovations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20stretch%20to%20say%20that%20in%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353828%2Fhow-indian-small-businesses-using-solar-power-clean-energy-renewable-energy-entrepreneurs-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20power%20has%20had%20a%20profound%20impact%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20villages.%20This%20impact%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20on%20small%20businesses%2C%20but%20also%20on%20the%20mindsets%20of%20people%20like%20Basanta.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20steps%20out%20for%20a%20walk%20in%20his%20village%2C%20he%20can%E2%80%99t%20ignore%20the%20unforgiving%20Manipur%20heat.%20This%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20hot%20summer%2C%20he%20thinks%2C%20vexed.%20Basanta%20has%20always%20loved%20the%20winter.%20But%20the%20heat%20will%20also%20mean%20more%20sunlight%20hours%2C%20which%20means%20more%20solar%20