ince%20then%2C%20the%20Pataudi%20Trophy%20has%20been%20the%20name%20of%20the%20India%20vs%20England%20bilateral%20contest%20played%20in%20England.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40594-sunil-manohar-gavaskar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20blasted%20the%20ECB%20for%20its%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20recent%20news%20that%20the%20ECB%20is%20going%20to%20retire%20the%20Pataudi%20Trophy%2C%20given%20to%20the%20winners%20of%20the%20Test%20series%20between%20England%20and%20India%20in%20England%2C%20is%20disturbing%20indeed.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20one%20has%20heard%20of%20a%20trophy%20named%20after%20individual%20players%20being%20retired%2C%20though%20the%20decision%20is%20entirely%20the%20ECB's%2C%20and%20the%20BCCI%20may%20well%20have%20been%20informed.%20It%20shows%20a%20total%20lack%20of%20sensitivity%20to%20the%20contribution%20made%20by%20the%20Pataudis%20to%20cricket%20in%20both%20England%20and%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20wrote%20in%20a%20column%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsportstar.thehindu.com%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Fipl-news%2Fsrh-batting-scoring-rate-ipl-2025-ind-eng-pataudi-trophy-retirement%2Farticle69422516.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESportstar%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20may%20well%20be%20a%20new%20trophy%20named%20after%20more%20recent%20players%2C%20and%20here's%20hoping%20that%20if%20an%20Indian%20player%20has%20been%20approached%2C%20he%20will%20have%20the%20good%20sense%20to%20politely%20decline%20%E2%80%94%20not%20only%20out%20of%20respect%20for%20two%20former%20India%20captains%20but%20also%20to%20avoid%20the%20same%20fate%20of%20having%20a%20trophy%20named%20after%20him%20retired%20after%20he%20is%20gone.%20The%20ECB%20is%20fully%20entitled%20to%20name%20the%20trophy%20after%20one%20of%20their%20own%20players%2C%20but%20I%2C%20along%20with%20loads%20of%20Indian%20cricket%20supporters%2C%20fervently%20hope%20that%20any%20other%20Indian%20cricketer%20will%20have%20the%20smarts%20to%20decline%2C%20lest%20history%20repeats%20itself%20as%20it%20has%20with%20the%20Pataudi%20Trophy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apparent%20move%20to%20'retire'%20the%20Pataudi%20Trophy%20has%20hurt%20Sharmila%20Tagore%2C%20actor%20and%20wife%20of%20the%20late%20Tiger%20Pataudi.%20%26quot%3BI%20haven't%20heard%20from%20them%2C%20but%20the%20ECB%20has%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20Saif%20that%20they%20are%20retiring%20the%20trophy%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharmila%20told%20HT.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20BCCI%20wants%20to%20or%20does%20not%20want%20to%20remember%20Tiger's%20legacy%2C%20it%20is%20for%20them%20to%20decide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECB%20has%20neither%20denied%20nor%20accepted%20the%20development.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20something%20we'll%20be%20able%20to%20offer%20you%20a%20comment%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20ECB%20spokerperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMansur%20Ali%20Khan%20Pataudi%2C%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20cricket%20captains%20India%20has%20produced%2C%20died%20in%20New%20Delhi%20in%2020211%20after%20battling%20with%20a%20lung%20infection.%20Pataudi%2C%20regarded%20as%20one%20of%20the%20finest%20Indian%20captains%2C%20played%2046%20Tests%20for%20the%20country%2C%20scoring%202793%20runs%20for%20an%20average%20of%2034.91%20with%20an%20unbeaten%20203%20being%20his%20highest%20score.%20In%20all%2C%20he%20smashed%20six%20centuries%20and%2016%20fifties%20in%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20retiring%20a%20trophy%20is%20not%20common%20in%20cricket%2C%20it%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20past.%20Like%20the%20Wisden%20Trophy%2C%20played%20between%20England%20and%20West%20Indies%2C%20which%20was%20renamed%20as%20Richards-Botham%20trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744026660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2