in-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152218.406-1744019551-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152218.406-1744019551-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418279%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESmoking%2C%20both%20active%20and%20passive%2C%20increases%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20cardiac%20disease%20at%20scale.%20Image%20credits%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fmrbo2ykgx5lt%2F22341%2F5535f080e1a7bb67f5fbb382d2295c7c%2Fcigarette-lung-bowel-inflammation.jpg%3F%26w%3D912%26fm%3Dwebp%26q%3D80%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFrontiers.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmoking%20causes%20vasoconstriction%2C%20which%20means%20the%20blood%20vessels%20become%20narrow%20and%20tight.%20This%20makes%20it%20harder%20for%20blood%20to%20flow%20freely%20and%20increases%20the%20chance%20of%20cholesterol%20and%20fat%20sticking%20to%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20arteries.%20Over%20time%2C%20this%20build-up%20%E2%80%94%20called%20plaque%20%E2%80%94%20can%20block%20the%20flow%20of%20blood%20to%20the%20heart%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20heart%20attack.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20who%20smoke%20have%20almost%20three%20to%20four%20times%20higher%20chances%20of%20having%20a%20heart%20attack%20compared%20to%20non-smokers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20role%20of%20diabetes%20and%20obesity%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20diabetes%20capital%20of%20the%20world%2C%20and%20its%20prevalence%20among%20younger%20people%20is%20rising.%20Dr%20Rao%20warns%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20now%20see%20diabetes%20cases%20appearing%20at%20just%2030%20years%20of%20age%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Rao%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20with%20diabetes%20have%20a%20significantly%20higher%20risk%20of%20developing%20heart%20disease%2C%20and%20vice%20versa%2C%20due%20to%20shared%20risk%20factors%2C%20such%20as%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20abnormal%20cholesterol%20levels%2C%20and%20damage%20to%20blood%20vessels%20caused%20by%20high%20blood%20sugar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObesity%2C%20particularly%20metabolic%20syndrome%2C%20is%20another%20major%20contributor.%20Metabolic%20syndrome%20refers%20to%20a%20cluster%20of%20conditions%20that%20occur%20together%2C%20increasing%20the%20risk%20of%20heart%20disease%2C%20stroke%2C%20and%20diabetes.%20This%20condition%20is%20an%20umbrella%20term%20for%20high%20cholesterol%2C%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20high%20blood%20sugar%2C%20and%20high%20body%20mass%20index%20(BMI).%20Dr%20Rao%20explains%2C%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20young%20people%20today%20have%20metabolic%20syndrome%2C%20which%20makes%20them%20more%20prone%20to%20heart%20attacks.%20Maintaining%20a%20BMI%20below%2024.5%20and%20reducing%20body%20weight%20by%205%25%20within%20three%20to%20six%20months%20can%20significantly%20reduce%20this%20risk%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20advises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20lifestyle%20factors%20are%20crucial%2C%20genetics%20also%20plays%20a%20role%20in%20many%20cases%20of%20heart%20disease.%20High%20LDL%20(low-density%20lipoprotein)%20cholesterol%2C%20often%20above%20190%2C%20is%20sometimes%20linked%20to%20familial%20hypercholesterolemia%2C%20a%20genetic%20condition%20that%20increases%20the%20risk%20of%20heart%20disease.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20person%20has%20a%20family%20history%20of%20heart%20disease%20before%2050%20years%20of%20age%20and%20has%20high%20cholesterol%20levels%2C%20it%20may%20be%20genetic.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20aggressive%20management%20is%20required%20through%20medications%20or%20newer%20injectable%20treatments%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Rao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDo%20not%20ignore%20these%20symptoms%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20challenges%20in%20diagnosing%20heart%20attacks%20in%20young%20people%20is%20the%20variation%20in%20symptoms.%20Traditional%20signs%20like%20chest%20pain%20are%20not%20always%20present.%20Dr%20Rao%20highlights%20some%20of%20the%20most%20common%20indicators%3A%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20often%20mistake%20prolonged%20chest%20pain%20for%20gastric%20issues.%20If%20pain%20lasts%20more%20than%2010%20minutes%20and%20is%20associated%20with%20sweating%2C%20jaw%20pain%2C%20or%20left-hand%20pain%2C%20it%20should%20be%20taken%20seriously%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T151844.373-1